                <h1>CAREERS</h1>
                <p>PARKnSHOP is the leading supermarket chain and food retailer in Hong Kong. We exceed our customer expectation through constant innovation and a commitment to delivering world-class standards of quality, freshness, service, range and value. In Hong Kong and Macau, we have over 300 stores with more than 10,000 employees. We look for passionate and committed talents who want to develop their careers in a fast moving environment with fascinating rewards.</p>
